TriggerLogic.Name: Custom Action (Alternate)
TriggerLogic.CodeStr: local units = Spring.GetTeamUnits(1) for i=1,#units do local unitID = units[i] local angle = math.random(0, 360) local heading = math.rad(angle) Spring.SetUnitRotation(unitID, 0, angle, 0) Spring.DestroyUnit(unitID, false, false) end
